OL,4,CSpecialist courts could be set up for
OL,5,Csex crimes
OL,6, Specialist courts should be set up to
OL,7, deal with the most serious sex crimes,
OL,8, a review has recommended.
OL,10,FThe national "trauma-informed" court
OL,11,Fwould have sentencing powers of up to
OL,12,F10 years imprisonment.
OL,14,FThe move is part of a proposed shake-up
OL,15,Fof how Scotland's courts deal with rape
OL,16,Fand other sexual offences cases.
OL,18,FOther proposals include the presumed
OL,19,Fuse of pre-recorded evidence and
OL,20,Fconsideration of a pilot scheme to hear
OL,21,Frape trials in front of a single judge.
